TopicTitle: [KSP 1.12.3] Atomic Tech Inc. Junkyards v.1.3 missing parts

Articles.Content:
Upgrading my version of Junkyards from 1.2.13 to 1.3 (via CKAN) causes ships that use "borrowedAltMk2" and "microCrewAtomicTech" parts to fail to load. I can downgrade back to 1.2.13 and these vessels load fine.  CKAN does not flag any conflicts. I'd love to move to v.1.3, but am clueless how to proceed. 

Thanks in advance!
